The paper deals with approximate analytics over compressed time series, which involves data management and analysis. Therefore, cs.DB (Database) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of linear algebra operators, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper discusses error guarantees, which is related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
